OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779221155
OL,3,CTeen e-biker jailed for killing great-
OL,4,Cgrandmother, 86, on zebra crossing
OL,6,FA teenager who rode an e-bike
OL,7,Fdangerously and knocked down and
OL,8,Fkilled an 86-year-old on a zebra
OL,9,Fcrossing has been jailed for six years
OL,10,Fand nine months.
OL,12,FBilly Stokoe, 19, was over the
OL,13,Fcannabis limit when he collided with
OL,14,Ffit and active Gloria Stephenson while
OL,15,Friding an illegal and defective
OL,16,Felectric Sur-Ron bike on the B1286
OL,17,FBurdon Road in Sunderland, on 16 May
OL,18,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
