PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779221155
OL,3,CTeen e-biker jailed for killing great-
OL,4,Cgrandmother, 86, on zebra crossing
OL,6,FHe held his mobile phone in his left
OL,7,Fhand despite the left-sided brake
OL,8,Fbeing the only one that worked,
OL,9,FNewcastle Crown Court heard, and rode
OL,10,Ffor half-a-mile in that manner.
OL,12,FDashcam footage showed he did not slow
OL,13,Fdown or try to avoid Mrs Stephenson,
OL,14,Fwho was walking her daughter's dog and
OL,15,Ftrying to complete her 10,000 steps a
OL,16,Fday when she was fatally injured on
OL,17,Fthe crossing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1779221155
OL,3,CTeen e-biker jailed for killing great-
OL,4,Cgrandmother, 86, on zebra crossing
OL,6,FStokoe was thrown off the bike but did
OL,7,Fnot stop at the scene, instead riding
OL,8,Foff to change his clothes and hide the
OL,9,Fmachine at a friend's house.
OL,11,FHe handed himself in at a police
OL,12,Fstation just over an hour later.
OL,14,FThe teenager was jailed for six years
OL,15,Fand nine months after he admitted
OL,16,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,18,FJudge Robert Adams said Mrs Stephenson
OL,19,Fwas a vulnerable road user on a
OL,20,Fpedestrian crossing who had waited for
OL,21,Ftraffic to stop for her and the dog.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
